Social Media Do’s and Don’ts

## ✅ Do’s
- Use strong and unique passwords for all accounts. 
- Keep your profile professional and updated. 
- Think thoroughly before posting personal content.
- Respect others and communicate politely. 
- Use privacy settings to control your information. 

## ❌ Don’ts
- Don’t share personal or sensitive information publicly. 
- Don’t click on unknown or suspicious links. 
- Don’t post offensive or inappropriate content.
- Don’t spread fake news or misinformation.  
- Don’t accept friend requests from strangers.
